ntil we accept self-criticism","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Hasan reported: A man said to Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cFear Allah, O leader of the believers! By Allah, the matter is not as you said!\u201d The people rushed to the man and they said, \u201cDo not criticize the leader of the believers!\u201d When Umar saw them\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32337,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/angels-guided-humility-kibr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34583,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Angels: Guided by humility, humbled by arrogance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no human being but that over his head are reins in the hands of an angel. If he is humble, it is said to the angel: Raise up his reins! If he is haughty,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28984,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/humility-does-his-own-chores\/","url_meta":{"origin":34583,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Humility: Whoever does his own chores is not arrogant","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe is not arrog